creator: Leonid Nikolayevich Andreyev
description:
LibriVox recording of The Little Angel and Other Stories by Leonid Nikolayevich Andreyev. (Translated by W. H. Lowe.)
Read in English by Larry Wilson; Mark Chulsky; VfkaBT; John Burlinson; Lynne Thompson; Mike Walker; Mary Schneider; Mike Pelton; Gaby; Shelf Worn; dbmcinnis
This is a volume of short works by Leonid Andreyev. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
subject: librivox; audiobooks;short stories; Russia
